1
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:13,000
[YUICHIRO panting]

2
00:02:13,083 --> 00:02:15,250
[BOTH panting]

3
00:02:15,333 --> 00:02:16,541
It can't be.

4
00:02:16,625 --> 00:02:17,666
Yuichiro?

5
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:19,041
[GUREN]
What are you waiting for?

6
00:02:19,125 --> 00:02:20,291
[BOTH gasp]

7
00:02:20,375 --> 00:02:23,291
Activate the curse
and kill him! Hurry!

8
00:02:23,375 --> 00:02:24,041
[YUICHIRO gasps]

9
00:02:24,125 --> 00:02:25,583
[GUREN]
That's an order!

10
00:02:25,666 --> 00:02:26,625
[gasps]

11
00:02:26,708 --> 00:02:28,125
--[panting]
--[YUICHIRO] I can't.

12
00:02:28,208 --> 00:02:30,958
[GUREN grunts]
You damn rookie!

13
00:02:31,041 --> 00:02:32,000
[GUREN grunts]

14
00:02:35,666 --> 00:02:38,541
[MIKAELA grunting]

15
00:02:41,791 --> 00:02:44,166
[YUICHIRO gasping]

16
00:02:44,250 --> 00:02:45,500
The hell?

17
00:02:46,750 --> 00:02:47,833
[GUREN]
What was that?

18
00:02:47,916 --> 00:02:50,958
You had him! Why didn't
you make the kill?

19
00:02:51,041 --> 00:02:53,041
Uh. I think he--

20
00:02:53,125 --> 00:02:56,166
[GUREN groans]

21
00:02:56,250 --> 00:02:59,541
[YUICHIRO]
Guren, are you all right?

22
00:02:59,625 --> 00:03:01,125
[YUICHIRO gasps]

23
00:03:01,208 --> 00:03:04,250
Worry about yourself, idiot! Did
you forget this is a war zone?

24
00:03:04,333 --> 00:03:05,833
Keep your eyes on the enemy!

25
00:03:05,916 --> 00:03:06,958
[YUICHIRO gasps]

26
00:03:07,041 --> 00:03:09,166
[MITSUBA]
Hey, moron, what's the deal?

27
00:03:09,250 --> 00:03:12,166
You had that bloodsucker
right where you wanted him!

28
00:03:12,250 --> 00:03:13,791
Did you forget how
to use your Gear?

29
00:03:13,875 --> 00:03:16,875
What's wrong?
You don't look so good.

30
00:03:16,958 --> 00:03:19,375
[GUREN groaning]

31
00:03:19,458 --> 00:03:21,458
Well, Yu?

32
00:03:21,541 --> 00:03:22,875
I'm sorry.

33
00:03:24,166 --> 00:03:26,291
But if that's who
I think it is...

34
00:03:28,375 --> 00:03:30,333
[YUICHIRO]
My family's with the vampires.

35
00:03:30,416 --> 00:03:33,541
[MIKAELA gasping]

36
00:03:33,625 --> 00:03:36,500
Tell me! Is it
really you, Mikaela?

37
00:03:36,583 --> 00:03:37,541
[MIKAELA grunts]

38
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:43,333
[ALL gasp]

39
00:03:43,416 --> 00:03:44,458
[YUICHIRO]
It is you.

40
00:03:44,541 --> 00:03:45,708
[ALL gasp]

41
00:03:45,791 --> 00:03:47,083
Mika.

42
00:03:47,166 --> 00:03:48,708
[crying]

43
00:03:48,791 --> 00:03:52,666
I'm... so sorry.
I abandoned you!

44
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:54,958
No. That's not true.

45
00:03:56,708 --> 00:04:00,083
[FERID] Aww. This might be the
sweetest thing I've ever seen.

46
00:04:00,166 --> 00:04:03,666
And just look at how much
dear Yuichiro has sprouted.

47
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:06,833
What a fateful and unexpected
reunion for the three of us.

48
00:04:06,916 --> 00:04:08,750
Brings back so many memories.

49
00:04:08,833 --> 00:04:11,833
It's almost enough to
bring tears to my eyes.

50
00:04:11,916 --> 00:04:13,708
So, what's the plan?

51
00:04:13,791 --> 00:04:17,250
Your friend is most likely being
manipulated by these humans.

52
00:04:17,333 --> 00:04:19,250
I'm going to save him.

53
00:04:19,333 --> 00:04:21,833
[FERID] From the hands
of these traitorous dogs?

54
00:04:21,916 --> 00:04:23,333
Yes.

55
00:04:23,416 --> 00:04:24,791
[FERID]
But he's one of them.

56
00:04:24,875 --> 00:04:27,083
Do you really think a
human could befriend us?

57
00:04:27,166 --> 00:04:29,125
I'm sure he'd rather die.

58
00:04:29,208 --> 00:04:31,000
[MIKAELA grunts]

59
00:04:31,083 --> 00:04:32,625
[FERID]
Ah! I know!

60
00:04:32,708 --> 00:04:36,250
I can do for him what
Krul did for you, Mika.

61
00:04:36,333 --> 00:04:39,208
One drop of my blood and
Yuichiro will be reborn.

62
00:04:39,291 --> 00:04:40,416
[MIKAELA grunts]

63
00:04:42,875 --> 00:04:46,666
If you so much as try to lay
a finger on him, I'll kill you.

64
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:48,750
Oh, come now,
I was only kidding.

65
00:04:48,833 --> 00:04:53,291
You really need to learn
to take a joke, my dear boy.

66
00:04:53,375 --> 00:04:56,666
Now, why don't I help
you rescue your princess?

67
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:58,083
I'll deal with
the other livestock

68
00:04:58,166 --> 00:05:00,916
while you rescue Yuichiro.

69
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,541
Just leave it to me.

70
00:05:02,625 --> 00:05:06,083
All you need to worry about is
getting him out of harm's way.

71
00:05:07,333 --> 00:05:09,666
[MIKAELA] I'm not surprised
you've made new friends.

72
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:12,416
You've always been
such a kind soul.

73
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:14,750
But sometimes you
can be too nice.

74
00:05:14,833 --> 00:05:17,708
So much so, that people
take advantage of you.

75
00:05:18,833 --> 00:05:21,208
[MIKAELA] The truth is,
these friends you've made

76
00:05:21,291 --> 00:05:22,500
are faking it.

77
00:05:22,583 --> 00:05:25,583
They're greedy and
deceitful. All of them.

78
00:05:32,041 --> 00:05:33,250
[FERID chuckles]

79
00:05:36,541 --> 00:05:39,500
Very well. It's been decided.

80
00:05:39,583 --> 00:05:40,875
All of the humans will die,

81
00:05:40,958 --> 00:05:43,791
except for the long
lost lamb, Yuichiro.

82
00:05:43,875 --> 00:05:45,875
[CROWLEY] Looks like I
got here just in time.

83
00:05:45,958 --> 00:05:47,041
[FERID grunts]

84
00:05:47,125 --> 00:05:49,250
Sorry I'm running late,
Third Progenitor.

85
00:05:49,333 --> 00:05:50,416
[FERID]
Ah, Crowley!

86
00:05:50,500 --> 00:05:52,666
So glad you could
make it to the party.

87
00:05:53,666 --> 00:05:54,833
Him again.

88
00:05:54,916 --> 00:05:57,500
I took a little detour
on the way over here.

89
00:05:57,583 --> 00:06:00,250
Of course. Was anything
interesting going on?

90
00:06:00,333 --> 00:06:01,541
[CROWLEY grunts]

91
00:06:01,625 --> 00:06:02,916
Well, now that you're here,

92
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:05,916
the game I had planned
won't be quite as much fun.

93
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:10,041
But, we could play a new one.
It's called "Take them alive."

94
00:06:10,125 --> 00:06:12,000
We'll capture the
Moon Demon Company

95
00:06:12,083 --> 00:06:13,875
and make them our livestock.

96
00:06:13,958 --> 00:06:15,250
I could get behind that.

97
00:06:15,333 --> 00:06:18,750
Damn. We were in trouble
before this guy showed up.

98
00:06:18,833 --> 00:06:20,083
I've got no choice.

99
00:06:20,166 --> 00:06:21,083
[GUREN groans]

100
00:06:21,166 --> 00:06:23,458
Everyone! Prepare to retreat!

101
00:06:23,541 --> 00:06:25,333
[BOTH gasping]

102
00:06:25,416 --> 00:06:27,416
No, we can't just
run away, dammit!

103
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:28,916
Mika's my family!

104
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,666
I won't leave him
with these monsters!

105
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:35,000
Shut up. You're willing to let
your comrades die for a vampire?

106
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,000
[YOICHI]
Yu!

107
00:06:39,791 --> 00:06:40,791
[KIMIZUKI grunts]

108
00:06:40,875 --> 00:06:41,708
Let's go.

109
00:06:41,791 --> 00:06:43,041
[YUICHIRO gasps]

110
00:06:43,125 --> 00:06:44,291
Please, Yu.

111
00:06:47,166 --> 00:06:48,625
[GUREN]
Fall back!

112
00:06:48,708 --> 00:06:51,083
Keep your formation and retreat
to the second defense line!

113
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,791
[FERID laughs]

114
00:06:54,875 --> 00:06:55,833
[ALL gasp]

115
00:06:56,833 --> 00:06:59,166
Come on, don't you wanna play?

116
00:06:59,250 --> 00:07:00,375
[GUREN]
Break formation!

117
00:07:00,458 --> 00:07:01,750
Damn you!

118
00:07:01,833 --> 00:07:02,791
[YUICHIRO gasps]

119
00:07:05,083 --> 00:07:06,916
[YUICHIRO yelling]

120
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,791
What the hell's
gotten into you?

121
00:07:08,875 --> 00:07:10,916
Die! You bastard!

122
00:07:14,708 --> 00:07:17,583
[yelling]

123
00:07:17,666 --> 00:07:18,958
[YUICHIRO grunting]

124
00:07:19,041 --> 00:07:20,000
Stop, Yu!

125
00:07:20,083 --> 00:07:21,875
What is that idiot thinking?

126
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,958
No, wait!

127
00:07:24,041 --> 00:07:26,375
[YUICHIRO grunting]

128
00:07:26,458 --> 00:07:29,750
You are fast, but you've
still got a lot to learn.

129
00:07:29,833 --> 00:07:31,208
[FERID gasps]

130
00:07:31,291 --> 00:07:32,833
[GUREN growls]

131
00:07:32,916 --> 00:07:34,041
--[YUICHIRO yelps]
--[GUREN grunts]

132
00:07:35,041 --> 00:07:36,916
[GUREN gasps]

133
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,333
And you should know by now

134
00:07:38,416 --> 00:07:41,583
that the injured lion's strike
is never quite as sharp!

135
00:07:41,666 --> 00:07:44,291
[GUREN grunts]

136
00:07:44,375 --> 00:07:45,791
Lieutenant Colonel!

137
00:07:45,875 --> 00:07:47,625
[SAYURI grunting]

138
00:07:47,708 --> 00:07:48,708
[LACUS]
Huh?

139
00:07:52,958 --> 00:07:53,791
Move.

140
00:07:53,875 --> 00:07:54,791
--[LACUS grunts]
--[SAYURI yelps]

141
00:07:58,541 --> 00:07:59,750
Why the hurry?

142
00:08:05,083 --> 00:08:07,583
Oh, wow. Still standing?

143
00:08:07,666 --> 00:08:09,916
Looks like we've got
ourselves a hero.

144
00:08:12,583 --> 00:08:13,833
Are you okay?

145
00:08:13,916 --> 00:08:16,333
Don't worry. I'll be fine.

146
00:08:16,416 --> 00:08:18,041
These bastards don't
have any intention

147
00:08:18,125 --> 00:08:19,500
of letting us get to Guren.

148
00:08:19,583 --> 00:08:21,625
In that case, we'll just
have to kill all of them.

149
00:08:21,708 --> 00:08:23,500
Easier said than
done, I'm afraid.

150
00:08:23,583 --> 00:08:25,958
That's why we're having all
this trouble in the first place.

151
00:08:26,041 --> 00:08:27,333
Huh?

152
00:08:27,416 --> 00:08:29,166
The only way out of here
is as livestock or corpses,

153
00:08:29,250 --> 00:08:31,083
so what's it going to be?

154
00:08:31,166 --> 00:08:31,750
[grunts]

155
00:08:31,833 --> 00:08:33,541
Well, we're waiting.

156
00:08:33,625 --> 00:08:35,041
--[SHINOA grunts]
--[VAMPIRE yelps]

157
00:08:37,333 --> 00:08:39,916
[MITSUBA yelling]

158
00:08:42,916 --> 00:08:43,875
[YOICHI grunts]

159
00:08:44,666 --> 00:08:46,000
[YOICHI grunting]

160
00:08:46,083 --> 00:08:47,041
[gasps]

161
00:08:49,250 --> 00:08:49,833
Focus!

162
00:08:49,916 --> 00:08:54,666
[KIMIZUKI grunting]

163
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:56,208
What are you doing?
Get on your feet!

164
00:08:56,291 --> 00:08:57,750
Yeah. Sorry.

165
00:08:57,833 --> 00:08:59,666
[CROWLEY]
Well, hello. So we meet again.

166
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:00,708
[KIMIZUKI gasps]

167
00:09:05,208 --> 00:09:07,833
This time, I'm not letting
you get away from me.

168
00:09:07,916 --> 00:09:09,375
[yelps]

169
00:09:09,458 --> 00:09:11,416
[GUREN groaning]

170
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:12,666
Guren!

171
00:09:14,041 --> 00:09:15,625
[yells]

172
00:09:15,708 --> 00:09:16,666
[gasps]

173
00:09:17,916 --> 00:09:18,791
Watch out!

174
00:09:18,875 --> 00:09:19,833
[gasps]

175
00:09:22,125 --> 00:09:24,500
I've waited so long to
get a taste of your--

176
00:09:33,916 --> 00:09:37,041
[FERID] You see? This is what
I meant about taking a joke.

177
00:09:38,666 --> 00:09:42,125
Be sure to call me
if you need a hand.

178
00:09:42,208 --> 00:09:44,125
[YUICHIRO]
Mika.

179
00:09:44,208 --> 00:09:46,500
[YUICHIRO yelping]

180
00:09:46,583 --> 00:09:47,916
[YUICHIRO gasps]

181
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:51,083
Let's go. Leave everything
behind and escape with me.

182
00:09:51,166 --> 00:09:54,833
Huh? What do you
mean escape? Answer me.

183
00:09:54,916 --> 00:09:56,833
Why're you with the vampire
who killed our family?

184
00:09:56,916 --> 00:09:59,000
[MIKAELA]
Nevermind that!

185
00:09:59,083 --> 00:10:00,041
[YUICHIRO gasps]

186
00:10:02,083 --> 00:10:03,041
Yu!

187
00:10:03,916 --> 00:10:04,875
[gasps]

188
00:10:04,958 --> 00:10:06,166
Don't take your
eyes off the enemy.

189
00:10:06,250 --> 00:10:07,208
[SHINOA grunts]

190
00:10:10,583 --> 00:10:13,583
[YUICHIRO] Hey, let go
of me! Stop playing, Mika!

191
00:10:13,666 --> 00:10:16,083
Tell me what's going on.
You at least owe me that much!

192
00:10:16,166 --> 00:10:18,666
The short version is that
you shouldn't be here!

193
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:21,000
Not with the humans.
They're just using you.

194
00:10:21,083 --> 00:10:23,583
[YUICHIRO] What? That's the
dumbest thing I've ever heard!

195
00:10:23,666 --> 00:10:25,625
Shut up and put me down!

196
00:10:29,708 --> 00:10:32,041
[YUICHIRO]
The humans are using me?

197
00:10:32,125 --> 00:10:35,958
What're you saying?
Aren't you still a...?

198
00:10:36,041 --> 00:10:37,000
[grunts]

199
00:10:47,625 --> 00:10:50,416
Wait. You are human, right?

200
00:10:50,500 --> 00:10:52,416
Don't tell me that
they changed you.

201
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:56,750
[gasps] Is this because of me?
Is this because I abandoned you?

202
00:10:56,833 --> 00:10:59,458
No! You didn't do
anything wrong!

203
00:10:59,541 --> 00:11:01,250
Then why, Mika?

204
00:11:01,333 --> 00:11:04,291
[MIKAELA] Let's just go.
It isn't safe here.

205
00:11:08,041 --> 00:11:10,708
Please, Yu. Come with me.

206
00:11:10,791 --> 00:11:11,833
[YUICHIRO gasps]

207
00:11:11,916 --> 00:11:13,958
No. I'm staying until it's over.

208
00:11:14,041 --> 00:11:17,666
It's just... they're
friends. I can't leave.

209
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:20,375
You're wrong! They only
see you as a tool!

210
00:11:20,458 --> 00:11:22,541
Please, Yu! Trust me!

211
00:11:22,625 --> 00:11:24,875
I'm trying to save you
before it's too late!

212
00:11:24,958 --> 00:11:26,041
[explosion]

213
00:11:26,125 --> 00:11:27,208
[YOICHI]
Shinoa!

214
00:11:27,291 --> 00:11:28,750
[gasps]

215
00:11:31,375 --> 00:11:34,500
[SHINOA groaning]

216
00:11:34,583 --> 00:11:36,166
Shinoa!

217
00:11:36,250 --> 00:11:36,875
[grunts]

218
00:11:36,958 --> 00:11:38,375
Please. Don't look back.

219
00:11:38,458 --> 00:11:41,666
There's nothing behind you.
Nothing important.

220
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,000
Just come with me!

221
00:11:43,083 --> 00:11:45,583
[yelps]

222
00:11:45,666 --> 00:11:46,916
[gasps]

223
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,583
Let go of her!

224
00:11:48,666 --> 00:11:52,125
[KIMIZUKI grunting]

225
00:11:52,208 --> 00:11:53,625
Come on!

226
00:11:53,708 --> 00:11:54,750
[MITSUBA yelps]

227
00:11:57,208 --> 00:11:59,000
They're in trouble!

228
00:11:59,083 --> 00:12:01,208
There's nothing you
can do to help them!

229
00:12:01,291 --> 00:12:02,416
Get off me!

230
00:12:02,500 --> 00:12:03,416
[BOTH grunting]

231
00:12:03,500 --> 00:12:05,500
You can't! Just
forget about them.

232
00:12:05,583 --> 00:12:08,000
In the end, they'll betray
you and toss you aside!

233
00:12:08,083 --> 00:12:11,291
[MITSUBA screaming]

234
00:12:11,375 --> 00:12:12,958
Mitsuba!

235
00:12:13,041 --> 00:12:15,541
Let's get out of here
before they capture you!

236
00:12:17,291 --> 00:12:19,083
[YOICHI gasping]

237
00:12:19,166 --> 00:12:20,958
I won't run away again!

238
00:12:21,041 --> 00:12:22,000
[MIKAELA yelps]

239
00:12:23,666 --> 00:12:24,583
[YUICHIRO grunts]

240
00:12:24,666 --> 00:12:26,083
[SHINOA groaning]

241
00:12:26,166 --> 00:12:28,958
Go, Yu. Run!

242
00:12:29,041 --> 00:12:29,791
[SHINOA grunts]

243
00:12:29,875 --> 00:12:31,541
Hush. Livestock don't speak.

244
00:12:31,625 --> 00:12:33,833
Please, call them
off! Hurry, Mika!

245
00:12:33,916 --> 00:12:35,541
You should be worried
about yourself.

246
00:12:35,625 --> 00:12:37,291
It's too late for them now.

247
00:12:40,083 --> 00:12:42,791
[SHINOA whimpering]

248
00:12:42,875 --> 00:12:47,958
[CROWLING slurping]

249
00:12:48,041 --> 00:12:50,250
[YUICHIRO grunts]

250
00:12:50,333 --> 00:12:54,541
[YUICHIRO screaming]

251
00:12:54,625 --> 00:13:00,416
[crying]

252
00:13:00,500 --> 00:13:02,666
Yu? What's the matter?

253
00:13:07,875 --> 00:13:08,833
[gasps]

254
00:13:31,083 --> 00:13:32,916
Talk to me, Asuramaru.

255
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:35,208
[ASURAMARU]
Hm? About what?

256
00:13:35,291 --> 00:13:37,208
What's happening to me?

257
00:13:37,291 --> 00:13:39,708
You're not trying to
possess me, are you?

258
00:13:39,791 --> 00:13:42,708
No. This has nothing
to do with me.

259
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:46,458
It seems we've got a
big problem on our hands.

260
00:13:46,541 --> 00:13:47,458
[YUICHIRO]
Huh?

261
00:13:47,541 --> 00:13:48,875
I've been around for a while,

262
00:13:48,958 --> 00:13:50,375
but I never thought
I'd be terrified

263
00:13:50,458 --> 00:13:53,458
of a monster inside the
human I was possessing.

264
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:57,458
There. You see how the
clouds are parting?

265
00:13:57,541 --> 00:13:58,916
It's as if the
heavens have opened

266
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:02,208
to shine judgment
on this cursed world.

267
00:14:02,291 --> 00:14:04,791
You know, I think
your friend is right.

268
00:14:04,875 --> 00:14:07,041
Listen to him and
escape while you can.

269
00:14:07,125 --> 00:14:09,916
This might be your
one and only chance.

270
00:14:11,541 --> 00:14:15,458
[ASURAMARU] If you stay here,
you won't be human for long.

271
00:14:15,541 --> 00:14:16,958
[gasps]

272
00:14:17,041 --> 00:14:17,875
Wait. What?

273
00:14:17,958 --> 00:14:20,083
--[horn blowing]
--[gasps]

274
00:14:20,166 --> 00:14:26,125
[horns blowing]

275
00:14:32,750 --> 00:14:35,125
[ASURAMARU]
I'm afraid it's too late.

276
00:14:41,458 --> 00:14:42,791
[ASURAMARU]
The non-human part of you

277
00:14:42,875 --> 00:14:45,000
is about to lose all control.

278
00:14:47,666 --> 00:14:50,333
[YUICHIRO yelping]

279
00:14:50,416 --> 00:15:00,541
[YUICHIRO screaming]

280
00:15:00,625 --> 00:15:05,916
[GUREN groaning]

281
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,666
And so it begins.

282
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:10,083
[SHINOA whimpering]

283
00:15:10,166 --> 00:15:16,583
[YUICHIRO screaming]

284
00:15:16,666 --> 00:15:20,458
It's true. The humans have
been using him all along.

285
00:15:22,333 --> 00:15:24,666
Snap out of it! Please, Yu!

286
00:15:24,750 --> 00:15:26,375
Leave this place with me!

287
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:41,125
[MIKAELA grunting]

288
00:15:43,125 --> 00:15:44,083
[CROWLEY]
Huh?

289
00:15:52,666 --> 00:15:54,666
[whimpering]

290
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:59,791
[CROWLEY] I don't know what that
is, but it doesn't look good.

291
00:16:01,625 --> 00:16:02,583
[grunts]

292
00:16:05,083 --> 00:16:06,041
[gasps]

293
00:16:10,125 --> 00:16:11,375
[CROWLEY whistles]

294
00:16:18,041 --> 00:16:20,875
That' a lotta damage.
Very impressive.

295
00:16:20,958 --> 00:16:23,458
[CROWLEY grunting]

296
00:16:25,083 --> 00:16:26,125
[CROWLEY grunts]

297
00:16:26,208 --> 00:16:28,583
--[YUICHIRO growls]
--[CROWLEY yelps]

298
00:16:28,666 --> 00:16:30,458
[CROWLEY grunting]

299
00:16:35,958 --> 00:16:38,166
No, Yu! Stop!

300
00:16:38,250 --> 00:16:39,291
[sighs]

301
00:16:39,375 --> 00:16:41,541
You went and got my
clothes all dirty.

302
00:16:42,666 --> 00:16:50,333
[CROWLEY grunting]

303
00:16:50,416 --> 00:16:51,375
[gasps]

304
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:15,666
[SHINOA yelps]

305
00:17:16,750 --> 00:17:17,833
[SHINOA gasps]

306
00:17:20,375 --> 00:17:21,500
[SHINOA gasps]

307
00:17:26,291 --> 00:17:28,375
[CROWLEY]
That's one creepy monster.

308
00:17:28,458 --> 00:17:29,916
Seriously, it's so revolting

309
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,958
I've completely
lost my appetite.

310
00:17:32,041 --> 00:17:33,041
[GUREN groaning]

311
00:17:33,125 --> 00:17:34,541
[CROWLEY]
What is that thing, Ferid?

312
00:17:34,625 --> 00:17:35,916
[FERID]
Hm.

313
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:38,833
I don't know. Do you?

314
00:17:38,916 --> 00:17:41,708
Nah. We'll just
have to wait 'n see.

315
00:17:44,166 --> 00:17:45,958
Let me guess,

316
00:17:46,041 --> 00:17:49,958
this is the result of human
experimentation, isn't it?

317
00:17:50,041 --> 00:17:51,291
Tell me,

318
00:17:51,375 --> 00:17:54,041
where does that infinite
greed of yours come from?

319
00:17:58,166 --> 00:18:00,000
[YUICHIRO groanss]

320
00:18:00,083 --> 00:18:01,000
[yelps]

321
00:18:01,083 --> 00:18:01,916
[GUREN groaning]

322
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,791
[FERID]
Honestly, it scares me.

323
00:18:03,875 --> 00:18:08,750
Besides, you always seem
to be losing control of it.

324
00:18:08,833 --> 00:18:09,875
See?

325
00:18:14,041 --> 00:18:16,291
[YUICHIRO groans]

326
00:18:16,375 --> 00:18:19,958
Sinners. Sinners must die.

327
00:18:20,041 --> 00:18:23,041
Sinners must all be annihilated.

328
00:18:23,125 --> 00:18:24,750
[SHINOA whimpers]

329
00:18:24,833 --> 00:18:26,333
No.

330
00:18:26,416 --> 00:18:27,375
[GUREN]
Shinoa!

331
00:18:27,458 --> 00:18:28,500
[SHINOA grunts]

332
00:18:28,583 --> 00:18:30,166
You're the only one
who can help him!

333
00:18:30,250 --> 00:18:32,291
There's still a chance
that he can come back!

334
00:18:32,375 --> 00:18:33,416
[gasps]

335
00:18:37,583 --> 00:18:39,500
[YUICHIRO roars]

336
00:18:43,125 --> 00:18:44,666
--[YUICHIRO growls]
--[SHINOA yelps]

337
00:18:50,083 --> 00:18:51,416
[SHINOA yelps]

338
00:18:51,500 --> 00:18:52,333
[gasps]

339
00:18:52,416 --> 00:18:53,083
[metal clangs]

340
00:18:53,166 --> 00:18:57,583
[MIKAELA groaning]

341
00:18:59,291 --> 00:19:01,083
No, Yu. Don't do it!

342
00:19:01,166 --> 00:19:03,750
You'd never be able
to forgive yourself!

343
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:10,583
Why? Why did you... save me?

344
00:19:10,666 --> 00:19:12,000
[MIKAELA]
Shut up, human.

345
00:19:12,083 --> 00:19:15,291
This is happening
because you used him!

346
00:19:15,375 --> 00:19:18,125
[MIKAELA grunts]

347
00:19:18,208 --> 00:19:21,166
[MIKAELA]
Damn it. My injury won't heal.

348
00:19:21,250 --> 00:19:25,208
[YUICHIRO]
Annihilate... every sinner!

349
00:19:25,291 --> 00:19:26,541
[YUICHIRO grunts]

350
00:19:26,625 --> 00:19:29,166
--[MIKAELA groaning]
--[SHINOA whimpering]

351
00:19:29,250 --> 00:19:30,166
[GUREN]
Shinoa!

352
00:19:30,250 --> 00:19:31,541
[SHINOA gasps]

353
00:19:31,625 --> 00:19:35,625
What're you waiting for?
Our lives depend on you! Go!

354
00:19:38,666 --> 00:19:39,625
[SHINOA grunts]

355
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:42,458
[SHINOA yells]

356
00:19:44,666 --> 00:19:47,333
Yu! Stop it!
Please, you have to!

357
00:19:47,416 --> 00:19:49,291
Or all of us are going to die!

358
00:19:49,375 --> 00:19:51,041
Don't you dare touch him!

359
00:19:51,125 --> 00:19:53,166
Get your filthy
hands off my family!

360
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:53,833
Stop it!

361
00:19:53,916 --> 00:20:00,791
[YUICHIRO screaming]

362
00:20:00,875 --> 00:20:02,041
[MIKAELA grunts]

363
00:20:02,125 --> 00:20:04,541
--[YUICHIRO groaning]
--[SHINOA whimpering]

364
00:20:04,625 --> 00:20:07,291
Please, Yu! Don't do it!

365
00:20:07,375 --> 00:20:11,000
[YUICHIRO yelling]

366
00:20:11,083 --> 00:20:13,041
Come back to us!

367
00:20:23,291 --> 00:20:24,250
[YUICHIRO gasps]

368
00:20:27,750 --> 00:20:28,541
[thud]

369
00:20:28,625 --> 00:20:32,875
[SHINOA]
Yu! I'm right here.

370
00:20:32,958 --> 00:20:38,000
[SHINOA crying]

371
00:20:38,083 --> 00:20:39,375
You're okay.

372
00:20:40,583 --> 00:20:42,791
Damn you humans
and your treachery.

373
00:20:42,875 --> 00:20:44,041
[grunts]

374
00:20:44,125 --> 00:20:46,125
You'll pay for this.

375
00:20:46,208 --> 00:20:48,375
[GUREN chuckles]

376
00:20:48,458 --> 00:20:50,291
So, how do ya like
my trump card?

377
00:20:50,375 --> 00:20:52,958
For a rookie, he puts
on one hell of a show.

378
00:20:53,041 --> 00:20:55,958
Sadly, for you, he didn't
really achieve anything.

379
00:20:56,041 --> 00:20:59,333
I wouldn't be so sure.
He's managed to distract you.

380
00:20:59,416 --> 00:21:02,708
And that was our main
objective all along.

381
00:21:02,791 --> 00:21:03,750
[FERID gasps]

382
00:21:09,958 --> 00:21:11,916
Uh-oh. They've seen us.

383
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:14,416
But not soon enough
to make a difference.

384
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:17,416
Destroy our enemies, Byakkomaru.

385
00:21:18,458 --> 00:21:21,333
[SHINYA] Oh, and try not
to hit Guren, okay?

386
00:21:21,416 --> 00:21:22,375
Boom.

387
00:21:23,958 --> 00:21:27,916
[roaring]

388
00:21:33,541 --> 00:21:36,416
[FERID] Whew. That was
too close for comfort.

389
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:37,916
If it hadn't been
for his big mouth,

390
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:40,833
I'd be a smoking pile
of ash right now. Uh.

391
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:53,291
It appears we're surrounded.

392
00:21:53,375 --> 00:21:54,958
[grunts]

393
00:21:55,041 --> 00:21:56,833
[KURETO]
Not bad, Lieutenant Colonel.

394
00:21:56,916 --> 00:21:59,458
I suppose junior branch
garbage has its use.

395
00:22:01,166 --> 00:22:04,791
You're done here. The Hiragi
family will be taking over.

396
00:22:04,875 --> 00:22:07,916
All right, men! I want
those nobles taken alive!

397
00:22:09,333 --> 00:22:10,833
[KURETO] We need to show
them, once and for all,

398
00:22:10,916 --> 00:22:14,458
what happens to anyone or
anything that opposes humanity,

399
00:22:14,541 --> 00:22:16,833
the Japanese
Imperial Demon Army,

400
00:22:16,916 --> 00:22:19,333
or the might of
the Hiragi family.

401
00:22:21,958 --> 00:22:23,208
Here we go.

402
00:24:04,708 --> 00:24:07,291
[YUICHIRO]
Next time, on Seraph of the End:

403
00:24:07,375 --> 00:24:09,000
"Everyone's a Sinner."

